<p>Oettingen, G., &amp; Mayer, D. (2002). The motivating function of thinking about the future: Expectations versus fantasies. Journal of Personality and Social Psychology, 83, 1198–1212. </p>
<p>Sarah G. (2018, December 4). Why Having a Crush Is Good for You. </p>
